    "46504": {
        "Desc": "Go to Dawn Winery",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Interrogate",
                    "T": "How did you find me here!? Favonian scum!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "I am no Knight of Favonius. Now, start talking! Your plan, what is it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Interrogate",
                    "T": "I see you received our letter... But if you think I'm going to let you in on our secrets, I'm afraid you're quite mistaken!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "Hmph. You appear to have misunderstood the situation you are in."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Burn him with <color=#00E1FFFF>Searing Hand</color>!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Interrogate",
                    "T": "D—Did you just use a Pyro Vision to shoot f—fire from your hands!? ...Aah! It burns!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "Let's see how long it takes for you to crack..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Burn him with <color=#00E1FFFF>Searing Hand</color> again!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Interrogate",
                    "T": "Stop! Stop! P—Please, the pain— I beg you... make it stop!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Burn him with <color=#00E1FFFF>Searing Hand</color> again!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Interrogate",
                    "T": "Ugh..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "Playing dead won't help you — that fire was nowhere near strong enough to— Oh... He seems to have <color=#00E1FFFF>passed out</color>..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "Hey! You sleep when I say you can sleep!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Interrogate",
                    "T": "Aah! It burns!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "<color=#00E1FFFF>Interrogate him</color> about their plan of attack."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Interrogate",
                    "T": "I'll talk, I'll talk! Ow ow ow... P—Please, stop! I'll tell you <color=#00E1FFFF>everything</color>!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Interrogate",
                    "T": "Th—The Abyss Order, we've amassed a force bound by a shared hatred for the Darknight Hero..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Interrogate",
                    "T": "They... They will march on the Mondstadt <color=#00E1FFFF>city gates</color> at 10 PM tomorrow night."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Interrogate",
                    "T": "That's everything I know... Please... Don't make me suffer those flames again..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "That's it? Well, I doubt you'd be foolish enough to keep anything else hidden."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "46505": {
        "Desc": "Tell Diluc about the war declaration",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Huffman",
                    "T": "If we do not make contact with the Darknight Hero soon..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What are we to do about the Abyss Order's challenge?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Huffman",
                    "T": "Ah, it's you two. I must admit, this issue of the Darknight Hero is proving to be something of a headache."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Huffman",
                    "T": "We've just held a meeting to decide on an appropriate course of action. Can you guess what it is?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Bury our heads firmly in the sand?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Huffman",
                    "T": "Haha... Good one. But no, the Knights cannot afford to simply stand by and watch while there is even the slightest inkling of a threat facing Mondstadt."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Huffman",
                    "T": "If that were the case, more and more people would start to rely on the Darknight Hero instead of the Knights of Favonius."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Join forces with the Darknight Hero?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Huffman",
                    "T": "No. That would send a signal that the Knights are in favor of the Darknight Hero's continued presence in our city... which we are not."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Huffman",
                    "T": "Encouraging this kind of individual heroism undermines the Knights' authority."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh. Well, what's the plan then?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Huffman",
                    "T": "Find out the Darknight Hero's true identity, and offer him our protection."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "\"Protection\"? He seems to be doing just fine without your protection so far, y'know..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Huffman",
                    "T": "Pff..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Huffman",
                    "T": "Well, since you've aided the Knights in the past, I might as well just tell you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Huffman",
                    "T": "The offer of protection is just a ruse, in order for the Knights of Favonius to take over full — and exclusive — responsibility for this matter."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "You aren't gonna let the Darknight Hero be all heroic and stuff? Why not?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Huffman",
                    "T": "Firstly, to show the might of the Knights of Favonius — to prove to the people that without the Darknight Hero, they can still rely on the Knights to maintain peace and harmony."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Huffman",
                    "T": "Secondly, the Abyss Order have no mercy in their hearts. If anything happened to the Darknight Hero..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Huffman",
                    "T": "It would only serve to further their nefarious ambitions."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Gosh... Paimon never knew the life of a knight involved so much untold anguish before."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Huffman",
                    "T": "But none of this will work if we don't establish the Darknight Hero's true identity in time."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "There's no need to despair, Huffman. Just follow my plan and everything will be fine."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Huffman",
                    "T": "Ah, Captain Kaeya."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "Lately, Master Diluc has been working the bar at the Angel's Share every night."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "All I need you to do is keep him in your sight. Think you can manage that for me?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Huffman",
                    "T": "Yes, Captain Kaeya! ...But, does that mean that..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Huffman",
                    "T": "Master Diluc is the Darknight Hero?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "Who knows...? It's just a hunch. I've been known to be wrong on occasion."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
