    "46609": {
        "Desc": "Wait until night (19:00 – 6:00)",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "Ah, you're back."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "Allow me to introduce the winery's master brewer—"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Connor",
                    "T": "So many Mist Flowers... Great! I can't wait to see how this turns out!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "So, are you certain the equipment can withstand this level of purity?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Connor",
                    "T": "Oh my... my goodness, the winery owner himself is addressing me directly!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Connor",
                    "T": "Don't worry, sir! It is always my honor to serve you, even if it means risking my life!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh? What's so life-threatening about this?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Connor",
                    "T": "Please excuse me — I must get to work!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What's he gonna do with a bunch of Mist Flowers?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "Long story short..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "A few days ago, the winery was experimenting with some new flavors. They wanted to see if Mist Flower can truly add a crisp and refreshing taste."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "Sure enough, they discovered that the flower's extract is truly potent."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "So the new batch is selling like hot cakes?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "No, not potent in terms of attracting customers, but slimes."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "Slimes need to extract elemental energy to survive... For them, this substance is simply irresistible."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "So I thought to myself, \"I wonder how much trouble I could cause now that I know this...\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Connor",
                    "T": "*bang crash wallop*..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Yikes! What was that noise?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Connor",
                    "T": "Ah... C—Cold... so c—cold... Master Diluc, purification complete, sir! B—But the equipment is..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "Marvelous work. Don't fret about the equipment, I shall have my butler order more immediately."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "\"Marvelous! Jolly-ho! Spiffing! Somebody fetch the butler!\" Paimon never knew you had to be so well-spoken to get a job in the alcohol industry."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "This is what I was talking about."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "Mist Flower extract... or for our purposes, \"Elemental Bait.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wow, it really has a strong elemental... whiff! Can we test it out?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Diluc",
                    "T": "Sprinkle a little on the ground over there — careful, just a small amount."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
